eztfl-html5 goals

Target question:
Given that I'm in London, England and walking down the road, use
the TFL Open Data API to answer the question: "I'm at X, Y walking
in direction Z. What are my bus stop options?"

Target devices:
Any compliant browser on any compliant device.
    + OS-dependent Apps are specifically avoided
    + Compliant devices will have location and direction available
    + Compliant browsers will have access to same via JavaScript

Target Screen resolution:
Assume all devices have a CSS displayport resolution of 1136x640
       + Other resolutions are a NICE2HAVE

Constraints:
HTTPS to be used between client and project
Make as much available as possible via github
Use old hardware, free software
